			<h2>Communicate on your schedule</h2>
			<p>It’s up to you how often you communicate. You can create, activate and share Tiles weekly to maximize engagement, or run campaigns at certain times of the year. Many administrators will create 4 to 8 Tiles during the week, and send them on the following Monday.</p>
