</section>

<section class="feature_sections" id="engagement">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="large-5 push-7 columns text_container">
			<h2>Trigger engagement</h2>
			<p>New Tiles are automatically organized into an email based on marketing best practices. In fact, digest emails like ours have a 148% higher click-through rate than non-digest emails (LaunchBit).</p>
			<p>The Board is totally private, only people you've added or shared your Board with using a unique link can join. When a user clicks on the email or unique link, they’ll be logged into the site and can start interacting with Tiles. The very first time users log-in, they’re asked to set a password.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large-7 pull-5 columns visual_container">
			<%= image_tag "marketing/more_info/digest_email_airbo.png", "alt" => "Digest email" %>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="feature_sections no_image_feature" id="reach_people">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="large-5 columns text_container">
			<h2>Reach people on any device</h2>
			<p>Airbo is automatically optimized for any device. That means users can access your Board on the go, even if they’re not at a computer all day.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large-7 columns visual_container">
			<h4>That's important because:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><span>61%</span> of cell phone owners in the U.S. have a smartphone (Pew Research Center)</li>
				<li><span>71%</span> of smartphone owners admit to using them at work (Google Insights)</li>
				<li><span>44%</span> of emails are opened on mobile (Litmus)</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="feature_sections" id="target_influence">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="large-5 push-7 columns text_container">
			<h2>Targeted social influence</h2>
			<p>As a user interacts with Tiles, an activity feed entry is created. Users can connect to one another to see their connection’s activities and create a scoreboard. Our data shows these mechanics increase user engagement by over 30%. Historically, up to 45% of participants join Airbo because a peer recruited them.</p>
			<p>Note that the Board doesn’t work like a typical social media site. There is no free text entry, which eliminates any administrative overhead for you.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large-7 pull-5 columns visual_container">
			<%= image_tag "marketing/more_info/activity-feed.png", "alt" => "Activity feed", "class" => "activity_feed" %>
			<%= image_tag "marketing/more_info/connections.png", "alt" => "Connections", "class" => "connections" %>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

